# Voice preview audio files

This directory holds pre-generated voice preview audio (one WAV file per
catalog voice, named `<voiceId>.wav`). The files are generated by
`scripts/generate-previews.js` and committed to the repo so the voice-server
`/preview` endpoint can serve them directly without hitting the Gemini TTS
API at runtime.

See `scripts/generate-previews.js` for regeneration instructions.
